# Copy to `scripts/.env.server` and adjust (gitignored locally).
# Operational clarity: Documentation/OPERATIONAL_DEPLOY_HOSTS.md
#
# Admin portal deploy (`admin-portal/deploy.sh`) rsyncs to FIN1_SERVER_IP.
FIN1_SERVER_IP=192.168.178.24
FIN1_SERVER_USER=io
#
# Parse Cloud deploy (`scripts/deploy-parse-cloud-to-fin1-server.sh`) uses
# FIN1_PARSE_CLOUD_SSH_HOST when set; otherwise 192.168.178.24 (WLAN = doc/API kanone),
# independent of FIN1_SERVER_IP so you can push static admin assets over Ethernet (.20)
# while keeping cloud deploy aligned with canonical docs unless overridden.
# FIN1_PARSE_CLOUD_SSH_HOST=192.168.178.20
#
# Finance / Technisch / Compliance Admin bootstrap (create-*-admin.sh):
# if BA_PASSWORD is not set in the shell, those scripts load scripts/.env.server and use BA_PASSWORD from there.
# One value per file — change before switching scripts, or pass BA_PASSWORD inline for each run.
# BA_PASSWORD=
